metadata.description:
**Must hold *[GraffitETH](https://www.niftygateway.com/marketplace/collection/0x7ba08e9d2b551a06cb3b76e3e76319f7790003ea)* to place bid.**  

The top 5 bidders will receive a physical copy of the postcard that inspired this work, which will be personalized with a unique message and a QR code that links directly to the numerical edition of your exact NFT.  

*Medium Shift* is photography combined with animated motion graphics design in After Effects.  
100% loopable 2.4K high-definition digital content. Looks great in a display frame.

Specs:  
2400px x 1600px  
H.264  
MP4
